---
title: ラバーバンドshop
pagination:
  data: goods
  size: 1
  alias: item
layout: layout.njk
permalink: 'item/{{ pagination.items[0].url | slugify }}/'
csspath: ../../css/
jspath: ../../js/
---
<div class="rababan rababan__flex">
  <div class="rababan__imagbox">
    <img class="rababan__img" src="../../images/{{item.itemphotos[0]}}" alt="">
    <div class="rababan__imglist">
      <img class="rababan__imgitem" src="../../images/{{item.itemphotos[0]}}" alt="">
      <img class="rababan__imgitem" src="../../images/{{item.itemphotos[1]}}" alt="">
      <img class="rababan__imgitem" src="../../images/{{item.itemphotos[2]}}" alt="">
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="rababan__box">
    <ul class="rababan__textbox">
      <li><h2 class="rababan__title">{{ pagination.items[0].name }}</h2></li>
      <li class="rababan__item">値段　{{ pagination.items[0].price }}円</li>
      <li class="rababan__item">Artist name　{{pagination.items[0].Artist}}</li>
      <li><p class="rababan__text rababan__item">{{pagination.items[0].text}}</p><li>
      <p class="rababan__text rababan__state">{{item.state}}</p>
      <li class="rababan__kazu">数量<input class="rababan__number" type="number" min="0" placeholder="個数の入力" value="0"></li>
    <li><a href="#" class="rababan__button">カートに入れる</a>
    <li class="rababan__attention">返品交換は受け付けておりません、ご了承ください。</li>
    <li class="rababan__attention">こちらの商品は受注生産限定となっております</li>
    <li class="rababan__attention">サービス手数料・送料で500円いただきます</li>
    <li class="rababan__attention">電子決済サービスは下記を対象にご使用いただけます。</li>
    <li class="rababan__kesai">paypay払い</li>
    <li class="rababan__kesai">d払い</li>
    <li class="rababan__kesai">FamiPay払い</li>


    </ul>
    
  </div>
</div>